    <briefdescription>
<para>A non-owning view over a contiguous sequence of JavaScript values. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>The view and all ValueWeak objects obtained from it are valid only while the underlying sequence remains alive and unmoved. All values must belong to the stored context; violating this precondition is undefined behavior. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
